312
00:14:49,756 --> 00:14:51,525 line:-2
except your parameter names
are written


313
00:14:51,592 --> 00:14:54,828 line:-2
as children of the parent
Parameters delimiter.


314
00:14:54.895 --> 00:14:56.830 line:-2 align:center
So now that
